### Prize Presets — Manage prize suggestion library

### List all prize presets (system + family custom)
GET {{host}}/api/prize-presets
Authorization: Bearer {{token}}

###

### Create a custom prize preset — copy id from response into http-client.env.json as prizePresetId
POST {{host}}/api/prize-presets
Authorization: Bearer {{token}}
Content-Type: application/json

{
  "label": "Ice cream",
  "emoji": "🍦"
}

###

### Delete a custom prize preset (admin only)
DELETE {{host}}/api/prize-presets/{{prizePresetId}}
Authorization: Bearer {{token}}
